ActJustice for Victims of Corrupt Foreign Officials Act (Sergei Magnitsky Law)
SubjectRegulations Amending the Justice for Victims of Corrupt Foreign Officials Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the JUSTICE FOR VICTIMS OF CORRUPT FOREIGN OFFICIALS REGULATIONS in order to add seven (7) individuals to the Schedule of the Regulations, ending their impunity and rendering them inadmissible to Canada unless otherwise authorized by the Minister of the Foreign Affairs.
